name: Garmin
description: Garmin Ltd. designs, develops, manufactures, markets, and distributes a range of wireless devices worldwide. The company offers running and multi-sport watches; cycling products; smartwatch devices; scales and monitors; Garmin Connect and Garmin Connect Mobile, which are web and mobile platforms where users can track and analyze their fitness, activities and workouts, and wellness data; and Connect IQ, enables third parties to create applications that run on Garmin devices. It also provides adventure watches; outdoor handhelds and satellite communicators; golf devices; consumer automotive; dog devices; InReach and Gramin response communication device; and Dive devices.
